\id 1TH NT0051.1T1 ONO Phinnemore NOV-1990.
\h 1 Tesalonaika
\toc1 1 Tesalonaika
\toc2 1 Tesalonaika
\mt1 1 Tesalonaika
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Paulo, Sailas, so Timoti, ŋedo ŋei ŋerep doku tau tau magu, Tesalonaika matko gemami, Anutu Magak so Waom Yesu Kristo wane ŋei ŋerep, ŋinane kibi iwa qemaine, wet menaŋ so peamŋo maine ŋinano payake.
\s1 Tesalonaika Magu Eŋane Gegeene So Mali Malipenane Pauloŋo Anutu Bakomine Kitoke.
\p 
\v 2 Ŋene naso baŋem korop ŋinane Anutu bakomine kito okanmaine, so ŋinane meŋe meŋenzo eŋetŋine ŋidora meŋenka okanmaine.
\v 3 Ŋene Anutuze so Magazane kaitko wetke ra wakone olat okanmaine, so yemo ŋine mali malipŋinane urataine mau paki wele maratka okanmami, wet maep ŋineŋo qebinŋungi mauluk mauluk urata togole ma okanmami, so wetŋine Waomze Yesu Kristo wano tako rakotka motpi paki tomaka gemami.
\v 4 Ŋene detmaine, kimakop, Anutuŋo wet maep okanŋungi paki, eŋine biŋek okanikei wane ŋibu tebaŋunge.
\v 5 Ŋedo Don Maine ŋinano ma ukone ea ŋidanŋem detpi weku wane donka mi okange, ŋo yemo zonominerop so Asu Koboboinerop weneŋ okange, so maki koto ŋino ea wane weleine wakonge, ŋene ŋinane keuo gege daleo gekone, ea ŋine mo detkamami, ŋine menanŋgei wane yale okangone.
\v 6 Ŋine ŋenane masi yewa mogare okangoi, so Waom wane masi yewa weneŋ mogare okangoi, so ŋine wikile zok manerop yaleka detkoi, paki ŋine Anutu wane don dere ma nogankakoi, yemo Asu Koboboineŋo simile qe watŋungi makoi.
\v 7 Ŋine yale okanbi paki Makedonia, so Akaia kepeo ŋine ŋei ŋerep mali malip korop gekoi, eŋe alakane ebone more, numaene sikan ongoi.
\v 8 Waom wane miti donŋo ŋinanoŋine sua ariki paki, Makedonia so Akaia kepeoka mi lotkeke, ŋo siluŋ ŋinane mali malipŋine Anutu wano pamaike, don yewaŋo yemo, mat korop rokopkeki, ŋei ŋerep korop eŋe detwarekoi, ea wane ŋene don mane ŋedo edangenane, kop mane mi okange.
\v 9 Ŋei ŋerep yewa, eŋe ŋene ŋinano sariŋem newanŋonbi paki, urata maŋem wele wakonge, ea wane donkisi ŋedan okanmami, sogine lopio ŋadekkau paki, Anutu wano takotke makatake more Anutu wele so gegeinerop eŋano ariu paki eŋane ŋei ŋerep magu wele okangoi.
\v 10 Paki eŋine Gipole, qeliwo ŋine sariakane tomaka gemami, eŋine Gipole Yesu eŋe seu seuo ŋine ma wisikae kaki wieke, eŋe gemage qeliwo ŋine sariake, yewao ŋene mapok ŋoniake.
\c 2
\s1 Pauloŋo Tesalonaika Matko Miti Urata Make
\p 
\v 1 Ŋine ŋidom mo detmami, kimakop, nae ŋine qeare ŋungole yewa wele midaine mi okange.
\v 2 Alakan Pilipi matko ŋengu kito okangoi, so dongo biraŋonbi, ŋene ŋado ŋinano Tesalonaika matko sarikone, ŋine ea mo detmami, ŋo ŋenane Anutuŋo yemo eŋinoŋine Don Maine sarike, yewa ŋine ŋidanikenane zonom ŋebongi, ŋene ŋaba eŋane kaet mi okangone, midakaka, ŋene sorin borin okane more ra wakone ŋidangone.
\v 3 Ŋene don ŋidanmaine, yewa dere siuk kutno mida, me wet siuk, me ŋene ikopka more ŋei natne mi isi ŋunmaine, midakaka!
\v 4 Ea wane turuŋine yemo ŋei naso baŋem Anutuŋo detŋongi ra okanmaine, onoka wane, eŋe ŋongi menaŋgi Don Maine iwa raikenane ra ŋebonge, ŋei edo ŋenane uratazane detpi, menageakane mida, Anutuŋo detki menageakane, oŋo ŋenane wetzane kine mo liwekka detka okanmaike.
\v 5 Ŋine mo detluk waremami, ŋene ŋinano sari more donzeŋo kelok mi okan ŋungone, me donŋo wesi aboŋ wane qom riwe riwe yewa mi kawetka ŋidangone, Anutuŋo ŋenane kine detlukmaike!
\v 6 Ŋene ŋei maneŋo eŋetze ŋedora mawa ŋoniake, me ŋido, me ŋei natne edo, ea wane mi rakone.
\v 7 Welekatne, ŋene Kristo wane aposolo gemaine, ea wane ŋido mawa ŋonikei wane ŋene maine ra ŋunŋem rap, ŋo siluŋ ŋene ŋinerop ketkele gekone, ketkele geŋem paki, nabokŋo medewekoune kito qesiŋ ebu okanmaike, rokop yalewa okan ŋungone.
\v 8 Onoka wane ŋene ŋinane simileze pakane, ŋene eweke more, ŋinerop Don Maine Anutu wanoŋine yewaka ŋidanikenane mida, ŋene gegeze ŋinane qikkaikenane weneŋ ewekkone, onoka wane ŋinane wetze zok pake ea wane!
\v 9 Welekatne ŋine mo detmami, kimakop, ŋene urata togogole wikilerop makone! Ŋene wikile ŋibonŋem bauŋine wayakane raŋem paki kaiweo, so ruo me sola wane urata weneŋ gereunerop makone, yewa mama mama so Anutu wanoŋine don Maine yewa weneŋ ŋidangone.
\p 
\v 10 Ŋine mo detmami, Anutu eŋe yaleka detmaike, ŋene ŋinanoken tanik manik maŋem ka more malip kakoi, yemo libeka, koboboine, so sot midaine.
\v 11 Ŋine detmami, Magak maneŋo eŋine gipon borasokoune okanon okanmaike, rokop yalewaka ŋedo ŋine okanŋunŋem paki, weku weku ŋibu don girem ŋidan warekone.
\v 12 Ŋene ŋidane ma togole ŋungone, ŋene wetŋine ma pesekone, so takotke gege ŋineŋo geu, Anutu kima okan kayakane qebin ŋungone, oŋo ŋidora newanŋune okanmaike, eŋinerop gekei wane, eŋine Gege Togon Mat Urumgo so qeli ewe zonom kotino.
\s1 Anutu Wane Don Dere Kumunam Kikoi
\p 
\v 13 Sogine ŋene Anutu bakomine kito okanikei wane ŋidangone, so kine mane iwa yale, ea wane ŋene yaleka naso baŋem Anutu bakomine kito okanmaine, ŋene Anutu wane don ŋinano ma sari ŋidanŋem, ŋine yewa detpi paki ma nogankakoi, yeo ŋei mane wane don yale midakaka, ŋo yemo Anutu wane don welekatne iwa pamaike, yewa ma nogan kakoi, Anutu eŋe malipka okanmami, ŋinane kotoŋino urata ma okanmaike.
\v 14 Ŋine, naŋane kimakopne, ŋinano masi tanik wakonmaike, masi tanik weku yewaka Anutu wane doku tau tau magu, Yuda kepeo gemami, eŋano wakonge, ŋei ŋerep yewa eŋe Kristo Yesu wane magu, ŋine ŋinŋine matŋine wekuo ŋine, ŋei yewa edo wikile ŋibonmami, rokop weku yewaka eŋe Yuda ŋei kimakopene edom wikile ebongoi.
\v 15 Eŋe Waom Yesu qeu paki propet engukoi, eso koso ŋene ŋengu esopŋon okanŋongoi, eŋe Anutu kima mi okanka okanmami, eŋe miti ŋei korop ŋabaon okanmami!
\v 16 Eŋe soringeu paki kitatŋongoi, ŋene qelaŋ ŋei miti don edanŋem, eaŋo koso ebuki maine menaŋgeu rap, masi yaline ma okangoi, iwa yemo sotene naso baŋem borikine kutno ma wakoi, paki yekuat namo Anutu wane busuŋo ŋado qoe kuteno wake pamaike, eaŋo enguki mida lelekei.
\s1 Paulo Eŋe Koso Manerop Qeare Oniakane Kake
\p 
\v 17 Eso ŋene qeliŋ ŋungone, yemo kimakop, wet korop mi qeliŋ ŋungone, yemo solaŋoka qeliŋŋune, nasomde bamgoka biraŋune gemaine, paki wetzeŋo yemo ŋinano pamaikane, ŋene koso ŋine manerop ŋunikenane zok urata suaine makone!
\v 18 Ŋene ŋinano koso zinge ukenane ŋonge, na Pauloŋo atakine atakine ukalane soringekole, ŋo Satanŋo qeliŋŋongi mi ukone, numa kitatŋonge.
\v 19 Ŋado korop yemo ŋine, natne eŋane ketkele midakaka! Ŋene wetze ŋinaneka pamaike, ŋene baŋ nasoo ge ari gekene eamo ŋinaneka, yemo kine iwa yale wane, Waomze Yesu Kristo ŋado koso zinge sariki, ŋenzarek orodoŋ kaitino okorakene, yewao ŋido ŋenane oi bakom kakapa suaine tebakau sariake.
\v 20 Welekakatne, ŋine ŋenane mawa mawaze so ŋenane oi bakomkopze!
\c 3
\s1 Pauloŋo Timoti Talekaki Tesalonaika Ma Togole Oniakane Arike
\p 
\v 1 Ŋene yewa koso kiroine mi ma okorakenane rokop okange, pakiso ŋene ŋenzeka Atens mesikenane rakone.
\v 2 Ŋo kimaze Timoti eŋe yemo talekaŋem uke, eŋe ŋenerop Anutu wane urata maki paki Kristo wane, Don Maine yewa ra okanmaike, ŋene talekaŋem ŋinano uke, yemo matogole ŋuniakane so mali malipŋine qesiŋkaki ma togolekeiwane.
\v 3 Paki, ŋinanoŋine natneŋo peleke more, mi zingekei, onoka wane wikile wakile so umat pamaike ea wane, ŋine ŋidom mo detmami, wikile wakile yaline yemo Anutu wane dereret sotakine, ŋene yalinerop okora urata maikenane detmaike.
\v 4 Ŋene ŋinerop gekone, naso yewao mo alakan ŋidane rakone, ŋene wikile wakile baŋ okanŋonikei, wane ŋine mo detluk waremami, ŋidangone ea wane rokop wakon waremaike.
\v 5 Na yalinane rawe paki, Timoti talekawe uke, na yewa maine mi ma okorawe rap, eso ea wane mali malipŋinane kine kayakane talekawe uke, welekatne, Liwe liwek ŋeiŋo mo liwek ŋungirap, paki kelok okan ŋunike, pakimo ŋenane urata ea, korop wele midaine okane, mida leleki rap, ea desikalane Timoti tale kawe uke.
\s1 Timotiŋo Donkisi Maine Masariki, Pauloŋo Wetpese Detke
\p 
\v 6 Timotiŋo ŋinano ŋine mo zinge ŋenano sari lotkike, eso eŋe ŋinane don kisi maine yewa ma sariki paki, mali malipŋinane so wet maep ŋinane don ŋedange. Ŋine naso baŋem ŋenane detpi menaŋ okanmaike, so ŋene ŋine ŋunikenane ŋon okanmaike, rokop yalewaka ŋine ŋene ŋonikei wane ŋun okanmaike, ea wane donkisi ŋedangi detwarekone.
\v 7 Eso umat kine kine so wikile wakileŋo kotozo wikile ŋebongi dere geŋem kimakop, ŋinane miti don ma gege ŋinane donŋo ma togoleŋonge, ŋinane mali malipŋineŋo ŋene ma togoleŋonge.
\v 8 Onoka wane, ŋine gegeŋine Waom wano motpi paki, togole okorakeiwo, ukude ŋene gege wele gekene.
\v 9 Ukude ŋene maine ŋinane raŋem paki, Anutu bakomine kitokene, ŋene eŋe bakomine kitokene, yemo onoka wane, ŋene ŋinane ra more wet menaŋ Anutuzane kaitko magemaine, ea wane.
\v 10 Kaiwe so ruo, ŋene eŋe ŋenze wetze kotineŋo korop olat okanmaine, yemo detŋongi uŋunŋem paki, mali malipŋine midawe raki, koso takotke ŋibongenane.
\s1 Miti Eŋano Wakone Pa Togoleakane Pauloŋo Meŋenkake
\p 
\v 11 Anutuze so Magaze oŋom, so Waomze Yesu Kristoŋo maine ŋenane numaze ma suatkeki ŋinano sarikene!
\v 12 Waomŋo ŋinane wet maepŋine maine maki, ŋidomka kima kima okangei, so ŋei ŋerep korop eŋane maki manerop suakei, paki kakapa okane ŋene ŋine wet maep okanŋun okanmaine, yale okanikei.
\v 13 Numa yalewa oken okangi paki, eŋe baŋ maki ŋinane mali malipŋine togoleake, so ŋine baŋ koboboine so libe qot qole okanikei, Anutuze so Magazane kaitko okorau Waomze Yesu sariake, eŋine so eŋane biŋek magukoune.
\c 4
\s1 Gege Koboboineŋo Anutu Kima Okankayake
\p 
\v 1 Kimakop, ŋine gege daleo geu, gegeŋine yewaŋo Anutu kima okan kayakane, ŋenano ŋine kau paki waetne makoi, numa yewa, yemo ŋine mo maine gemami, pakimo iwa yemo ŋene koso ra ŋunmaine, so qebin ŋunŋem, ŋine Waom Yesu wane eŋetko koso manerop okanikei.
\v 2 Ŋene suaineze, Yesu wane eŋetko don kine kine korop ŋidangone, eamo detwaremami.
\v 3 Anutu wane simileŋo yemo, ŋinane iwa yale dere ŋibon okanmaike, eŋe ŋine koto ŋine libe libe geu paki, borikine yau yaup mama bailalaŋ yewa qeliŋkalukkei wane ra okanmaike.
\v 4 Ŋei bonep bonep ŋine iwa yale desikei, ŋanom weku eaŋo, koto ŋino libe libe so, ewe kito kito ea wane numao okorakene.
\v 5 Bailalaŋ mane wetke more misuk, qelaŋ edo Anutu mi detkau paki okanmami, yale misuk okanikei.
\v 6 Yalinao ŋei maneŋo kimaine ŋerep wane ra misuk matali kayake, me ea wane misuk isi kayake, ŋene don iwa yemo mo alakan ŋidangone, ŋene togoleka girem don ŋidane rakone, borikine yaline maikei, ŋei yewa eŋe Waomŋo baŋ turuŋine eboniake.
\v 7 Anutuŋo kotoze dika gekenane mi ŋedora newanŋonge, midakaka, kotoze libe libe gekenane newanŋonge.
\v 8 Ea wane ŋei mane eŋe don iwa ŋadek kayakeo, eŋe ŋei mi ŋadek kayake, eŋe Anutu, Asuine koboboine ŋibon okanmaike eŋe ea mo weneŋ ŋadek kayake.
\p 
\v 9 Ŋine miti don dere mali malip korop okangoiŋo, kimakop ŋine wet maep okanonikei wane, don zok mi qe ŋibonikene, Anutu oŋom kimakop ŋine wet maep daleo okan onikei, ea wane kine mo kito ŋibonge.
\v 10 So ŋine kimakopze korop Makedonia kepeo ge arimami, numa yaleoken okan wet maep okan onmami, ŋo siluŋ kimakop, ŋene koso manerop okanlukeu suayakane qebin ŋunmaine.
\v 11 Ŋine wet dereret ŋine togogole motpi paki, ari sari so don ukat mi okane more mat ŋino doŋmane metlukeu paki, meteŋineŋo ŋinŋine urata mauluke maikei paki, gegeŋine maratkaikei, ŋene alakan don ŋidangone yale okangei.
\v 12 Ŋine numa yaleoken okanbi, qelaŋ eŋe ŋune eweŋine kitokei paki, ŋine kine kine mane wane mi ŋaŋaekei.
\s1 Waom Sarikane Don
\p 
\v 13 Kimakop, ŋene ŋei seukkoi, eŋane don welekatne iwa ŋidanŋem detpi paki, mitiene midaineŋo wetborik okan okanmami, yale misuk okanikei.
\v 14 Ŋene detlukmaine, yemo Yesu eŋe seukki paki koso wisikae wieke, wane ŋene detlukmaine, yemo ŋei Yesu malipkau paki eŋe Anutuŋo baŋ Yesurop weneŋ ebuki gege togongo arikei.
\p 
\v 15 Iwa yemo Waom eŋine don ŋine ŋidanŋem detpi, wisikaune gemami ŋene Waom sariake, naso yewao ŋei alakane seukkoi, eŋe yuan one more ŋedo baŋ lewine mi alakanikene.
\v 16 Yewao yemo bokawoka suaine bokaki, aŋelo suainane don wakongi, Anutu wane romon taron wakone paki, Waom eŋine baŋ qeliwo ŋine sari kesiake paki, ŋei mo sogino Kristo detlukkau paki seukoi, edo gege togon wane alakane wisikae wiekei.
\v 17 Wieu, ŋene wisikaune gekeneŋo, naso yewao korop baŋ qeturage eŋerop weneŋ kezoŋ kutno wa keuo Waom marat kaikene, paki ŋene baŋ Waom gorop banine tako rakot ge arikene.
\v 18 Ea wane ŋine don iwaŋo wetŋine ma peseŋungi wet maep okan nagu gekei.
\c 5
\s1 Waom Sariakane Masuatnagukene
\p 
\v 1 O, kimakop, iwa yemo kaiwe ma nasoo, masi kine kine iwa wakoniake, ŋine mi ŋaŋaemami, wanemo mi qe ŋibonikene.
\v 2 Ŋine ŋidom kine mo detlukmami, Waom sariakane Naso yemo kobu mama ŋei maneŋo goigo sanka sari okanmaike, yalewa sariake.
\v 3 Ŋei ŋerep qelaŋ eŋe raikei, “Kine kine korop yemo qamen sororokmaike, so maine,” paki, eaka kine kine kaetneropŋo baŋ engu matali oniake! Eŋe baŋ mi kakakka arikei, eamo baŋ ŋerep mane medep mayakane gae poradaŋ so maki qisemaike, yale okanoniake.
\v 4 Ŋo ŋine, kimakop, yemo panaman koto mi gemami, Wane Waom wane Naso yewaŋo poradaŋ so, ŋibuki kobu mama ŋei yale mi qisekei.
\v 5 Ŋine ŋei ŋerep korop yemo qelaŋan wane biŋek, ŋine kaiwe wane biŋek, ŋene ruo goiŋ wane biŋek midakaka, me panaman wane biŋek midakaka.
\v 6 Eso ea wane ŋene ŋei natne eŋe kulu pau qesiŋone more ŋene kulu seu seune misuk paikene, ŋene wet wisika diamze maŋem paki kotozane sawe gekene.
\v 7 Goiŋ keremaike, naso yewao ŋei ŋerep eŋe kulu pa okanmami; goiŋ keremaike, naso yewaoka ŋei ŋerep eŋe doku togole neu paki wet siuk ma wakone okanmami.
\v 8 Ŋo ŋene kaiwe wane biŋek okangoneŋo, yemo kotozane sawe gekene. Ge more mali malip so wet maepŋo sukukuze okangi, biraŋem ket kawet ŋoniake, paki wetzeŋo mena menaŋ wane dere tebaka gege yewaŋo marokze okangi biraŋem ket qorot ŋoniake.
\v 9 Anutuŋo eŋine wet gerepinane wikile marat kaikenane mida, yemo Yesu Kristo wane raki paki, mena menaŋ wane welaine okangenane ŋebuke,
\v 10 oŋo ŋenane ra seukkane ŋene eŋerop weneŋ wekuoka gekene, wisikaune gemaineo, me seu seu marat kaikeneo eŋe sariake naso yewao qeturaŋ ŋoniake.
\v 11 Ea wane ŋine iwa okane gemami, yale okanbi paki auye matogole qetogole okanikei, so kito qe qesiŋ okan nagu gekei.
\s1 Naŋ Qeqe Don So Mosop Don
\p 
\v 12 Ŋene ŋine qebin ŋunmaine kimakopze, yemo ŋinane keu ŋino wikile urata mamami, eŋe mauluke eweene kitou paki aŋaene tewekkei, ŋeiwa Waomŋo alakane ŋibonikei so sikan ŋunikei wane ma wakon onge ea qesiŋonkei.
\v 13 Eŋane detpi zok manerop wayake, so wetmaep okan onikei, onoka wane eŋe urata ŋinano mamami, ea wane, ŋinŋine keuŋino yemo peamka paki gekei.
\p 
\v 14 Ŋene togoleka qebinŋunmaine, kimakopze, Ŋine ŋei taboŋ bau wawa gemami, eŋe don girem edanikei, ŋei kaet gege kito qesiŋ okanonikei, ŋine ŋei korop eŋe bororom okanonikei.
\v 15 Ŋine ŋinano ŋine kau ŋei maneŋo borikinane turuŋ mako makok misuk okaniake, ŋo ŋine naso baŋem yemo wetŋine weku motpi paki, ŋine ŋidomka mauluk nagu gekei, so ŋei natne korop okanonikei.
\p 
\v 16 Wet menaŋ kutno naso baŋem ge arikei.
\v 17 Meŋe meŋen gorop naso baŋem gekei.
\v 18 Kine kine korop yewa wane bakom kito kito okane gekei, iwa yemo Anutuŋo ŋido gegeŋine Kristo Yesu wano paki, yale okane gekei wane ra ŋune okanmaike.
\p 
\v 19 Naso Asu Koboboineŋo kine kine mane maikei wane ma wisikae ŋungi, ŋine leŋka more misuk qewoloŋgei.
\v 20 Anutu wane Asu wane pidon ŋidanbi misuk dere ŋadek kaikei.
\v 21 Kine kine korop dere qe wazae warekei, maine yewamo magekei.
\v 22 Eso borikine kine kine yemo ŋadekkaikei.
\p 
\v 23 Anutu peam ŋebo ŋebon wane kine welaine, oŋom ŋinane wisika gegeŋine maki eŋino ariki sauke mauluk okan ŋungi korop kuneneŋ maine okan warekei, paki warekaki wet dereret so sola korop sot midaine mayakatneka ge mageŋem, Waomze Yesu Kristo koso zinge sari lotkeake.
\v 24 Eŋe oŋom ŋidora newan ŋunmaikeŋo baŋ yewa okanŋoniake.
\p 
\v 25 Kimakop ŋenane yaleka meŋenkaikei.
\p 
\v 26 Kimakopze korop eŋe mete au au okan warekei.
\p 
\v 27 Na ŋine ra qebin okanŋunmaile, Waomzane eŋetko, wane ŋine kibi iwa kimakopze doku tau tau magu ŋei ŋerep korop dapore edanbi desikei.
\p 
\v 28 Waomze Yesu Kristo wane mena menaŋŋo ŋinano pa ari payake. 
